sentences.english: Jiaozhou Bay, which is much smaller, is found to the south, next to Qingdao.
sentences.chinese: 而半島以南緊挨青島的膠州灣，則要小得多。

sentences.english: Jiaozhou Bay and its adjacent area are getting more and more important in the economic and social development of Tsingtao city.
sentences.chinese: 膠州灣及其鄰區在青島市經濟和社會發展中日趨重要。

sentences.english: Local wetlands serve as a key attraction for migratory birds arriving at Jiaozhou Bay.
sentences.chinese: 當地溼地是候鳥飛來膠州灣的主要吸引力。

sentences.english: This paper describes some observations made mainly on the growth of raftculturedmussels (Mytilus edulis L. ) in Jiaochou Wan, Shandong Province.
sentences.chinese: 本文報道了膠州灣貽貝生長的研究結果。

sentences.english: The investigate of distribution of integron in multidrug resistance isolates in Jiaozhou Bay was carried out.
sentences.chinese: 爲調查整合子在膠州灣水域多重耐藥菌中的分佈情況。

sentences.english: In this article, we analyzed the content d several heavy metal in the surficial sediment of Jiaozhou Bay, and discussed the source, distribution.
sentences.chinese: 本文分析了膠州灣表層沉積物中幾種重金屬的含量。
